23#include "mpfr-impl.h"
24
25void
26mpfr_set_prec_raw (mpfr_ptr x, mpfr_prec_t p)
27{
28 MPFR_ASSERTN (MPFR_PREC_COND (p));
29 MPFR_ASSERTN (p <= (mpfr_prec_t) MPFR_GET_ALLOC_SIZE(x) * GMP_NUMB_BITS);
30 MPFR_PREC(x) = p;
31}
